e control en el mayor general. 
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\f36\fs20\lang3082\langfe11274\langnp3082 \loch\af36\dbch\af0\hich\f36 \'bc\tab}}\pard \ql \fi-360\li1068\ri0\sl240\slmult0\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx360\jclisttab\tx1068{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\ilvl0\ls16\pnrnot0
